[30;1m31 | [0m[35mclass GenerateAnswerNodeKLevel(BaseNode):[0m
[30;1m32 | [0m[35m    """[0m
[30;1m33 | [0m[35m    A node responsible for compressing the input tokens and storing the document[0m
[30;1m34 | [0m[35m    in a vector database for retrieval. Relevant chunks are stored in the state.[0m
